        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2995941870" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer782011384391029999"><strong>A compelling story</strong><br/><br/>I thoroughly enjoyed this book. A great glimpse of the reality of heroin addiction from both the addict and her mum. <br/>Their shared story did everything it was supposed to. I felt the romance of the high, the frustration of feeling helpless as a mother. I felt uncomfortable at times and hopeful in others. <br/>Overall I highly recommend this book. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

