      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/21556255-thin-wire-a-mother-s-journey-through-her-daughter-s-heroin-addiction">Trivia About Thin Wire: A Moth...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
        <div class="mediumText">No trivia or quizzes yet. <a href="/trivia/work/21556255-thin-wire-a-mother-s-journey-through-her-daughter-s-heroin-addiction">Add some now &raquo;</a></div>
